[ch (id=scripting_api) [title Scripting API]

    This chapter lists specific PDML functions available in script nodes.

    The functions are divided into two categories:
    [list
        [el [header PDML API]
            The [i PDML API] provides functions used to interact with the PDML document.
        ]
        [el [header Core API]
            The [i core API] provides a set of general functions used to work with text files and URLS, interact with the operating system, run external programs and OS scripts, interact with the user, etc.
        ]
    ]

    [u:ins_file path=01_PDML_API.pml]
    [u:ins_file path=02_core_API.pml]
]
